    <title>Changing Effects Order</title>
    <media type="image" src="figures/effectsorder.png" its:translate="no"/>
    <p>
        You can change the plugins order in the effects chain. Just click on the up and
        down arrows next to the plugin name. The first plugin from top to bottom is the
        first to receive the audio signal.
